| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0398 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5cefa7a3-755b-59e0-a2e2-90088f7c6b89"
